body:
For mental health awareness month we should be sending well wishes to Dan and to each other.


My well wish to you: Change is not immediate and recovery is possible. I know you can do it. If you’re struggling my inbox is open. I want you to be okay. I believe in you. I love you. We’ll get through this together. I promise. ❤️

Watch how Dan comes back from hiatus with a law degree, like he probably saw in the news that Kim Kardashian was going for one herself and so he just went, “fuck it, I’m going back to uni and finishing this god damn thing that I started ages ago”

Either that or he’s secretly joined his brother in jogging around the world.
